            "title": "Getting items 🎯",
            "content": "Use square brackets `[]` with the index number.\n\n`fruits[0]` is 'Apple'.\n`fruits[1]` is 'Banana'.",
            "codeSnippet": "let colors = ['Red', 'Green', 'Blue'];\nconsole.log(colors[0]); // Red\nconsole.log(colors[2]); // Blue",
